		<h2>List of contributions</h2>
		<ul>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2018/index.html">SLE 2018</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2018/paper12.html">Continuous model validation using reference attribute grammars</a></em> (<a href="../profile/JohannesMey.html">Johannes Mey</a>, <a href="../profile/RenéSchöne.html">René Schöne</a>, <a href="../profile/GörelHedin.html">Görel Hedin</a>, <a href="../profile/EmmaSöderberg.html">Emma Söderberg</a>, <a href="../profile/ThomasKühn.html">Thomas Kühn</a>, <a href="../profile/NiklasFors.html"><span class="info">Niklas Fors</span></a>, <a href="../profile/JesperÖqvist.html">Jesper Öqvist</a>, <a href="../profile/UweAßmann.html">Uwe Aßmann</a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2018s/index.html">SLE 2018 SI</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2018s/paper01.html">Relational Reference Attribute Grammars: Improving continuous model validation</a></em> (<a href="../profile/JohannesMey.html">Johannes Mey</a>, <a href="../profile/RenéSchöne.html">René Schöne</a>, <a href="../profile/GörelHedin.html">Görel Hedin</a>, <a href="../profile/EmmaSöderberg.html">Emma Söderberg</a>, <a href="../profile/ThomasKühn.html">Thomas Kühn</a>, <a href="../profile/NiklasFors.html"><span class="info">Niklas Fors</span></a>, <a href="../profile/JesperÖqvist.html">Jesper Öqvist</a>, <a href="../profile/UweAßmann.html">Uwe Aßmann</a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2020/index.html">SLE 2020</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2020/paper12.html">Principles and Patterns of JastAdd-style Reference Attribute Grammars</a></em> (<a href="../profile/NiklasFors.html"><span class="info">Niklas Fors</span></a>, <a href="../profile/EmmaSöderberg.html">Emma Söderberg</a>, <a href="../profile/GörelHedin.html">Görel Hedin</a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2021/index.html">SLE 2021</a>)</span> Served on <a href="https://conf.researchr.org/committee/sle-2021/sle-2021-papers-program-committee">PC</a></li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2022/index.html">SLE 2022</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2022/paper13.html">Property Probes: Source Code Based Exploration of Program Analysis Results</a></em> (<a href="../profile/AntonRisbergAlaküla.html">Anton Risberg Alaküla</a>, <a href="../profile/GörelHedin.html">Görel Hedin</a>, <a href="../profile/NiklasFors.html"><span class="info">Niklas Fors</span></a>, <a href="../profile/AdrianPop.html">Adrian Pop</a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2024/index.html">SLE 2024</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2024/paper05.html">Efficient Demand Evaluation of Fixed-Point Attributes using Static Analysis</a></em> (<a href="../profile/IdrissRiouak.html">Idriss Riouak</a>, <a href="../profile/NiklasFors.html"><span class="info">Niklas Fors</span></a>, <a href="../profile/JesperÖqvist.html">Jesper Öqvist</a>, <a href="../profile/GörelHedin.html">Görel Hedin</a>, <a href="../profile/ChristophReichenbach.html">Christoph Reichenbach</a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2024s/index.html">SLE 2024 SI</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2024s/paper09.html">Property probes: Live exploration of program analysis results</a></em> (<a href="../profile/AntonRisbergAlaküla.html">Anton Risberg Alaküla</a>, <a href="../profile/GörelHedin.html">Görel Hedin</a>, <a href="../profile/NiklasFors.html"><span class="info">Niklas Fors</span></a>, <a href="../profile/AdrianPop.html">Adrian Pop</a>) </li>
